overview:
Barsatie Enterprise - Wealth Institute Online is a multi-national marketing organization of independent business owners whose goal is to provide its business partners with the best training, support and inspiration in their efforts to better themselves personally, while pursuing financial independence by empowering others with aspirations of greatness. Simply stated, “People helping people”.

By forming a network, we create a strong international collective where borders, politics and religion are separated from each other. We as a collective recognize that there are many professionals in industries that are dumped after years of hard work, because of the bad economy. We also see a magnifying trend in the fact that 50 + unceremoniously fired because they are too expensive. Also there are many highly educated young people who do not get a job despite years invested to have a once-respected degree.

Conclusion: We are part of a well-established network of experienced entrepreneurs to help others in our society who have no experience in building a passive income by giving our support in addition to what they do now. We call this building your plan B next to your Plan A. Our mission is to help as many people to have a strong plan B so that fewer families will get hit hard by the current and future economic developments.
